"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"● Define stable currency as systemic risk\\n\\n● Classify stablecoins into securities\\n\\n● Define stable currency as a monetary fund\\n\\n● Put forward bank-level regulatory requirements for stablecoins\\n\\nThe report also stated that the standards and plans for the regulation of stablecoins are already under development.\\n\\nCentralized stablecoins have a clear legal subject and need to cooperate with traditional finance in asset custody, channels, etc., which is less difficult to supervise, and may be the first project facing impact in the DeFi field.\\n\\nFrom another perspective, when a centralized stablecoin is included in the regulatory framework, it is very likely to open a window of opportunity for the decentralized stablecoin that has been behind it, allowing it to be actively adopted by more users and protocols.\\n\\nOf course, in the long run, it is impossible for the regulators of various countries to give up the supervision of decentralized stablecoins, but because the supervision of decentralized projects is more difficult, and the supervision falls on centralized stablecoins and decentralized stablecoins. The time difference is enough to leave precious time difference and catch up space for the latter.\",\"timestamp\":1634578711,\"title\":\"U.S. regulators may initiate supervision of stablecoins from the following aspects\"},\"digest\":\"vTAvt9GwEprd1dSkFRxPgKX8iDIMyAkNvOfJBtCfijQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xC7dF240e00F248C48E765ac9d25e2A6c71253999\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"5zg4LXHEsCnAZwvpaWGuobz0lmxFoShT9tJt6WlwdY8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"JQgUh3ZTCFj4bMGyX0iVHzHs17lU78vd7_Lac0H7ETc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Rz0eG5xkzJqdtFRZm3jhuBHotpZdi9EKxdXoYp9Ei6bMkTjEqbtOS7esP3taD8wAAndx_YxP2Ui96wPR4iRK3w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x42a38989b45d6bfb63f434d366469fe49c1091a08112d192bf3a30921afffdfa52f7f37a260da70be05dd6a4edfc6